\par }{\insrsid14682107\charrsid10442657 The plaintiff\rquote s claim against the defendant is for a declaration that the assessment of Shs.83}{\insrsid10442657\charrsid10442657 , 848,380}{\insrsid14682107\charrsid10442657 
