\par From the records, the plaintiff}{\insrsid3161750\charrsid10442657 
 is a trading entity, trading in fuel and lubricants, export of coffee, cocoa and other lines of trade.  It is registered for Value Added Tax.  It is not disputed that for the period March 2000 to June 2005, the plaintiff 
submitted a VAT refund claim of Shs.116,234,856= and as a result the defendant commissioned an audit to ascertain the basis of the claim.  At the end of the audit exercise, an assessment for Shs.83}{\insrsid10442657\charrsid10442657 , 848,380}{
