\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid10442657 {\insrsid465789\charrsid10442657 The parties accordingly agreed that the plaintiff\rquote s claim would be Shs.26}{
\insrsid10442657\charrsid10442657 , 892,568}{\insrsid465789\charrsid10442657 = if the invoices relating to the fuel/lubricants business were admitted by the defendant.  By implication and agreement, all other claims are unsustainable.
\par 
\par The parties agreed that it was not necessary to lead oral evidence on the matter.  I accepted that position.  The defendant\rquote s denial of the invoices is based on three grounds:
