That the known registered VAT tax payer and hence rightful claimant for tax refund is the plaintiff herein, Bakwany}{\insrsid9584719\charrsid10442657 e}{\insrsid465789\charrsid10442657  Trading Company Limited.
\par 2.\tab That the invoices submitted to support the VAT refund claim in respect of the fuel/lubricants business were issued to Caltex Rwenzori }{\insrsid14500961\charrsid10442657 SS A/C Bwambale and Star Service Station \endash 
 Kasese which entities are not known to the defendant.}{\insrsid465789\charrsid10442657 
